This </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">innovative design enables material to flow around the core pins, significantly reducing material usage and the need for secondary machining operations.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:15px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:15px;">  •  </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Tonnage Range:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The LSP Series is available from 220 to 1600 tons, catering to a wide range of forging needs. This </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">innovative design enables material to flow around the core pins, significantly reducing material usage and the need for secondary machining operations.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:15px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:15px;">  •  </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Tonnage Range:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The LSP Series is available from 220 to 1600 tons, catering to a wide range of forging needs. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Eccentric Dual Plunger Design:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series boasts a unique eccentric dual plunger mechanism that ensures direct force delivery to the workpiece. This design minimizes off-center loads, resulting in superior part quality and extended die life. The two plunger guides deliver tonnage vertically, unlike traditional crankshaft-style presses, which are prone to side thrust loads.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Tonnage Range:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> With a robust tonnage range from 330 to 2200 tons, the EHW Series is versatile enough to handle various applications, from intricate electronic components to large automotive parts.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>I-PRESS® Control System:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> At the heart of the EHW Series is the I-PRESS® control, the most advanced press and automation control available. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Eccentric Dual Plunger Design:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series boasts a unique eccentric dual plunger mechanism that ensures direct force delivery to the workpiece. This design minimizes off-center loads, resulting in superior part quality and extended die life. The two plunger guides deliver tonnage vertically, unlike traditional crankshaft-style presses, which are prone to side thrust loads.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Tonnage Range:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> With a robust tonnage range from 330 to 2200 tons, the EHW Series is versatile enough to handle various applications, from intricate electronic components to large automotive parts.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>I-PRESS® Control System:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> At the heart of the EHW Series is the I-PRESS® control, the most advanced press and automation control available. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. The I-PRESS® also enables real-time monitoring of critical parameters such as oil temperature, flow rates, and valve positions, ensuring your press operates within the desired parameters for maximum productivity.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><B>Applications and Versatility:</B></SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">The HP1 is not just a press; it’s a solution to many forming challenges.
